# CYBERDUDEBIVASH SENTINEL APEX v134.0.0 — Cloudflare Pages header contract
# Forces charset=utf-8 on every HTML response and applies security hardening
# headers. Edit only via PR — this file is the single source of truth for
# static asset response headers.

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload

/*.html
  Content-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600

/reports/*
  Content-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600
  X-Robots-Tag: index, follow

/api/*
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Cache-Control: no-store

/*.json
  Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *

/*.js
  Content-Type: application/javascript; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400

/*.css
  Content-Type: text/css; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
